---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Hubungi Kami - KiraFaraid"
  description="Hubungi pasukan KiraFaraid untuk pertanyaan, cadangan, atau melaporkan ralat pada kalkulator faraid kami."
>
  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 space-y-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-emerald-800 mb-4">
      <!-- Mail icon -->
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-8 h-8"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Hubungi Kami</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="prose prose-slate text-sm max-w-none">
      <p>Kami sentiasa berusaha untuk menambah baik KiraFaraid. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang pertanyaan, cadangan, atau menemui ralat pada sistem, sila hubungi kami.</p>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Email:</p>
          <p class="text-emerald-600 mb-4">admin@kirafaraid.my</p>

          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Alamat Surat Menyurat:</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            KiraFaraid Team<br />
            Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
          </p>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-500">
          Nota: Kami adalah pasukan pembangun perisian dan bukan peguam syarie. Soalan berkaitan hukum agama yang kompleks sebaiknya diajukan terus kepada pejabat agama berhampiran anda.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-3">Pautan Berkaitan</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-900 bg-emerald-50 hover:bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition font-medium no-underline">Kalkulator Faraid →</a>
          <a href="/panduan-faraid" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-900 bg-emerald-50 hover:bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition font-medium no-underline">Panduan Faraid →</a>
          <a href="/dasar-privasi" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-900 bg-emerald-50 hover:bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition font-medium no-underline">Dasar Privasi →</a>
          <a href="/terma-perkhidmatan" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-900 bg-emerald-50 hover:bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition font-medium no-underline">Terma Perkhidmatan →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
